short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Simplifies entry of credit applications from One Dealer Lane into lender portals.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
One Dealer Lane's Quick Fill Extension Tool allows you to save time and minimize data entry errors in submitting credit applications to your lender's submission portals. 

The ODL Quick Fill Extension Tool will take applications that have been collected using One Dealer Lane and populate those details into your lender's credit application forms directly.
